ant-collaboration/">亚航 VTuber 代理机构 Project Kavvaii 通过与机上餐厅合作庆祝人才</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“亚航的 VTuber 机构 Project Kavvaii 通过机上餐厅合作庆祝人才” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/airasia-vtuber-agency-project-kavvaii-congratulates-affiliated-talents-airi-gwynevere-and-mikazuki-mai-on-their-in-flight-restaurant-collaboration/embed/#?secret=IsULSinlD4#?secret=qJ7p3hr6PL" data-secret="qJ7p3hr6PL" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.airasia.com/projectkavvaii/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">卡瓦伊计划</a></p><cite>亚洲航空</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/airasia-vtuber-agency-project-kavvaii-2-talents-to-graduate-on-march-31-2024/">亚航 VTuber 机构 Project Kavvaii 的两名人才将于 3 月 31 日毕业的帖子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/airasia-vtuber-agency-project-kavvaii-2-talents-to-graduate-on-march-31-2024/feed/ 0 117113
